.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地要返shift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a8c4cca9897ccaf5a563310e1b1863dcbf34f7","tid":1836832,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b6bd0d0293ee662914af0fff5a87fbb7579e79e","tid":1836832,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢地覺得後生既垃圾冇用身子弱先要戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n只要你係佢面前除低口罩，對住佢咳幾聲或者打乞痴<br />\n班傻閪即刻神情有異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:28:34.000Z","msg":"香港班廢中廢老唔戴口罩係因為佢地覺得自己<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個頭近</span></span>，唔使怕。"}]}